        <div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:8px;">Timber</h3>
          <p>The main character. A 13-year-old Sheltie-Husky mix adopted at age 10 from a shelter in northwest Indiana — proof that a dog can become a full-blown content star later in life. Full costume changes, dramatic close-ups, and a flair for theatrics that makes every post feel like a scene.</p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Costume &amp; lifestyle content</span>
