          <h3 style="margin-bottom:8px;">Harvey</h3>
          <p>The sidekick. A 4-year-old mystery-box mutt with big, loveable, high-energy vibes who shows up in plenty of Timber's content — from costume duos to everyday outings. Adopted from the same northwest Indiana shelter as Timber, and just as camera-ready.</p>
